data.description: A move-in-ready home awaits you in Anna's vibrant Park Place neighborhood within Anna ISD. Situated on a spacious corner lot, this residence is conveniently close to major highways (US 75, TX 121, Collin County Outer Loop, US 380) and offers easy access to Anna ISD schools, shopping, restaurants, parks, and playgrounds. With 3 bedrooms, formal dining, and two full bathrooms, the primary bedroom boasts dual vanities, a garden tub, a separate shower, and a large walk-in closet. Enjoy a huge backyard and a luxurious upgraded kitchen with stainless steel appliances, electric stove with oven and dishwasher, island kitchen with granite countertops, all open to a bright family room and breakfast area featuring ceiling fans. Ideal for investors and primary home buyers, don't miss out on this great opportunity.
